Peter Duncan (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Duncan_(actor) 0 Peter Duncan (born 3 May 1954) is an English actor and television presenter. He was a presenter of Blue Peter in the 1980s, and made a series of family travel documentaries between 1999 and 2005. Peter_Duncan ( born 3_May_1954 ) is an_English_actor_and_television_presenter .
